Grammar

    0 $accept: program "end file"

    1 program: constdecls forstatement

    2 constdecls: constdecls constdecl
    3           | constdecls metadatastreamdecl
    4           | ε

    5 metadatastreamdecl: METADATASTREAM LESS intlit COMMA intlit GREATER id SEMICOL

    6 constdecl: type id ASSIGN intlit SEMICOL
    7          | NOPT type id ASSIGN intlit SEMICOL
    8          | type id ASSIGN LCURLY intlist RCURLY SEMICOL

    9 intlist: intlit COMMA intlist
   10        | intlit
   11        | ε

   12 forstatement: FOR LPAREN constdecl expr SEMICOL unarystmt RPAREN LCURLY forstatement RCURLY
   13             | FOR LPAREN constdecl expr SEMICOL unarystmt RPAREN LCURLY innernest RCURLY

   14 outstatements: outstatements outstatement
   15              | outstatement

   16 innernest: outstatements
   17          | ifstatement
   18          | switchstatement

   19 ifstatement: IF LPAREN ISEVEN id RPAREN LCURLY outstatements RCURLY ELSE LCURLY outstatements RCURLY
   20            | IF LPAREN id LESS id RPAREN LCURLY outstatements RCURLY ELSE LCURLY outstatements RCURLY
   21            | IF LPAREN id LESSEQUAL id RPAREN LCURLY outstatements RCURLY ELSE LCURLY outstatements RCURLY
   22            | IF LPAREN id GREATER id RPAREN LCURLY outstatements RCURLY ELSE LCURLY outstatements RCURLY
   23            | IF LPAREN id GREATEREQUAL id RPAREN LCURLY outstatements RCURLY ELSE LCURLY outstatements RCURLY
   24            | IF LPAREN ISEDGE id RPAREN LCURLY outstatements RCURLY ELSE LCURLY outstatements RCURLY
   25            | IF LPAREN ISEDGE id OR ISEDGE id RPAREN LCURLY outstatements RCURLY ELSE LCURLY outstatements RCURLY
   26            | IF LPAREN ISEDGE id AND ISEDGE id RPAREN LCURLY outstatements RCURLY ELSE LCURLY outstatements RCURLY
   27            | IF LPAREN PAD id id id id RPAREN LCURLY outstatements RCURLY ELSE LCURLY outstatements RCURLY

   28 switchstatement: SWITCH LPAREN id RPAREN LCURLY casestatements RCURLY

   29 casestatements: casestatement casestatements
   30               | casestatement

   31 casestatement: CASE COLON outstatements

   32 outstatement: OUT ASSIGN expr SEMICOL

   33 type: INT

   34 expr: expr CROSS expr
   35     | expr LESS expr
   36     | expr STAR expr
   37     | expr MINUS expr
   38     | term

   39 unarystmt: loc POSTINC

   40 term: factor
   41     | LPAREN expr RPAREN

   42 factor: intlit
   43       | loc

   44 intlit: INTLITERAL

   45 loc: id
   46    | id LBRACKET id RBRACKET

   47 id: ID


